Subject: Exported times not consistent from AIC.
Description: In AIC under Activity Details I see the access time which looks like is in EST format. If I export that it is 6 hours ahead. At first I thought it was UTC but that is only 4 hours ahead of EST. I attached screenshots.
Solution_Comment__c: I explained to the customer that we get access time from the server we are scanning. It's UTC from that server's local time.
